<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="down-adj">down <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /daʊn/    美 /daʊn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>沮丧的；情绪低落的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tim’s been feeling down because of his low test scores.
因为考试分数不高，蒂姆最近情绪很低落。</p></div></div>